      "review_summary": "The PR opts Control UI sidebar/session-list and chat session picker `sessions.list` calls into `includeDerivedTitles`, adds `derivedTitle` to the UI session row type, and falls back to it in the shared display-name resolver with tests.\n\nPR surface: Source +7, Tests +49. Total +56 across 7 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. from source inspection. Current main does not request `includeDerivedTitles` in the Control UI sidebar/picker paths, and the PR still leaves the picker option-label helper unable to render `derivedTitle`-only rows.",
